<MELItem itemNbr="27-61-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-27-61-01.1.2-27-61-01">
<Title>Speedbrake Lever Position Transducers</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="B" nbrInstalled="4" nbrRequired="3" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Automatic speedbrake function operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Speedbrakes are verified to operate normally before each landing.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>An additional inflight failure may affect landing performance.</Para>
</Note>
<Para>Prior to every landing, verify speedbrake operation.</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Confirm SPEEDBRAKE ARMED memo message annunciation when speedbrake lever is set to ARMED on approach.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>In the event SPEEDBRAKE ARMED memo message is not displayed, speedbrakes (both auto and manual) may be inoperative for landing.  Landing distance will be increased:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Increase normal configuration landing distance by 20%.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Increase non-normal configuration landing distance by 35%.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
